reviewText: Wonderful film. Nostalgic and well acted.
A Walter Brennan classic, and fun to watch.
Great old movie filmed in Hunt Valley in my home state of Maryland!
DVD arrived in fine condition n plays fine.

Maryland, what can I say.  Another wholesome family movie.  I thought I would never see this movie again in life, much less own it.  It hasn't been on tv in years.  But the old movies are not on television anymore, so thanks again amazon.
